}

<div class="container">

    <div class="row">

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-xs-6">
            <h1>The Best Trios</h1>
            <img src=".\img\Wolfmother.jpg" width="350" />
            <p>
                This page is dedicated to some of the best three-person bands in the world. Based on my own
                professional music experience, it is difficult to throw down that kind of sound with only three
                individuals playing.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-8 col-xs-6">
            <ul>
                <li><h4>The Beastie Boys</h4><p>Hip-Hop Legends</p></li>
