                <li><h4>Cream</h4><p>Eric, Jack, and Ginger</p></li>
                <li><h4>Wolfmother</h4><p>Will make your ears bleed!</p></li>
                <li><h4>Rush</h4><p>Three dudes making that sound!</p></li>
                <li><h4>The Jimi Hendrix Experience</h4><p>Hendrix? Need I say more?</p></li>
                <li><h4>Primus</h4><p>Les</p></li>
                <li><h4>The Stray Cats</h4><p>Gonna rock this town!</p></li>
                <li><h4>Los Lonely Boys</h4><p>Tres hermanos</p></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
